<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Enabling High Throughput for Mass Adoption</h3>



<p>To achieve mass adoption, Polygon dApps stand out through their key features that enable high throughput, allowing for efficient and scalable processing of transactions.</p>



<p>One of the standout features is the integration of Polygon&#8217;s zkEVM, which combines the security of Ethereum with the low transaction costs of zkRollups. This unique approach significantly enhances the <a href="https://securenest.org/learn/polygon-dapps-scalability">scalability of dApps built on Polygon</a>, making them capable of handling a high volume of transactions without compromising on security.</p>



<p>Additionally, Polygon&#8217;s Proof of Stake (PoS) validators play a crucial role in ensuring fast transactions at near-zero gas fees, further enhancing the platform&#8217;s appeal for mass adoption.</p>



