<p>Yes, Polygon&#8217;s ecosystem tools have some limitations. While they offer a wide range of flexibility, certain types of dapps may face constraints due to the platform&#8217;s design. However, Polygon is continuously evolving to address these limitations.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How Does Polygon Dapps Ensure Seamless Integration With Existing APIs and Third-Party Services?</h3>



